<taxonomicName id="4C394D7B043AFFFDFCC8F8ECFC57763A" authorityName="Hansson" authorityYear="2022" box="[800,924,1808,1832]" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Diglyphomorphomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="329" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="costulata">
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFCC8F8ECFC57763A" box="[800,924,1808,1832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">D. costulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFC42F8EDFC7C763A" bold="true" box="[938,951,1808,1832]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">5</emphasis>
body in lateral view, holotype; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFB10F8EDFACE763A" bold="true" box="[1272,1285,1808,1832]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">6</emphasis>
body in dorsal view, holotype; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFED1F8C9FE94765E" bold="true" box="[313,351,1844,1868]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">7–8</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C394D7B043AFFFDFE84F8C8FE13765E" authorityName="Hansson" authorityYear="2022" box="[364,472,1845,1868]" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Diglyphomorphomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="329" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cristata">
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFE84F8C8FE13765E" box="[364,472,1845,1868]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">D. cristata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFE0EF8C9FE38765E" bold="true" box="[486,499,1844,1868]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">7</emphasis>
body in lateral view, paratype; 
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFCDAF8C9FCF4765E" bold="true" box="[818,831,1844,1868]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">8</emphasis>
body in dorsal view, holotype.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="8B8636F8043AFFFDFF2FF887FD7F76AA" blockId="8.[151,1437,1914,2013]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">
Variation in 
<typeStatus id="5482885A043AFFFDFEBBF886FE7C7687" box="[339,439,1915,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">paratype</typeStatus>
. Length 
<quantity id="4CC19B1D043AFFFDFDF1F886FDA07687" box="[537,619,1915,1941]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="329" unit="mm" value="1.8">1.8mm</quantity>
. Fore wing submarginal vein with six setae on dorsal surface. Propodeal callus with nine setae. Otherwise as in 
<typeStatus id="5482885A043AFFFDFDA3F863FD7A76AA" box="[587,689,1950,1976]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8636F8043AFFFDFF2FF83EFE4376CE" blockId="8.[151,1437,1914,2013]" box="[199,392,1986,2013]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">
<emphasis id="B94DEAEA043AFFFDFF2FF83EFECF76CF" bold="true" box="[199,260,1987,2013]" pageId="8" pageNumber="329">Male</emphasis>
. Unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
